description:
Building a better rock show at Loophole:
-Book NYC’s force majure post hardcore art rock powerhouse YHWH Nailgun for their debut show in Berlin;
-Add the Dedstrange Records signed local treasure Data Animal to ensure the numbers are appropriately animalistic and accurate;
-Invite Kaspars Groševs who runs the renowned 427 Gallery in Rīga, to contribute caulked and sealed artwork and;
-Nicely but firmly, said while looking directly in your eyes: please come.
